HEADWORD: Graham bread
<hw>Gra"ham bread"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[From Sylvester
<ets>Graham</ets>, a lecturer on dietetics.]</ety> <def>Bread made of
unbolted wheat flour.</def> <mark>[U. S.]</mark>
